personalInfo.education: Texas A&M University (Agriculture Leadership and Development, 2012)

tourBios.carHigh:
2015: Had two top-25s and five cuts made in 8 starts on PGA TOUR Latinoamérica, where he finished the season ranked 96th on the Order of Merit... Best finishes were T15 at the Dominican Republic Open in June and T16 at the Ecuador Open in September.

2014: Finished the PGA TOUR Latinoamérica season ranked 45th on the Order of Merit… Had two top-10s and five top-25s in 8 starts… Did not miss a cut… Best finish was T4 at the season opening 67th Arturo Calle Colombian Open, where he carded four rounds in the 60s, including his season low 64 on the last day… A T10 at the Guatemala Stella Artois Open was his other top-10 finish… Teamed-up with Brad Hopfinger to finish T4 at the inaugural Bridgestone America's Golf Cup in Buenos Aires, Argentina in October… Made the cut in all three of his starts on the Web.com Tour, with a T54 finish as his best at the Stonebrae Classic in early August.

2013: Played six events on the Adams Golf Pro Tour, making the cut in each of them… Best finish came at the Young Life Abilene Open, where he was the runner-up… Finished T113 at the Web.com Tour Qualifying Tournament to earn conditional status for the 2014 season.
tourBios.otherCarHigh: Played college golf at Texas A&M, where he was a member of the team that won the 2009 NCAA Division I National Championship… Was a 2010 Honorable Mention All-American… Was a 2011 second-team All-American... Was on the All-Big 12 team between 2010-12... Finished as runner-up at the 2012 Northeast Amateur and the 2012 Western Amateur... Semifinalist at the 2011 U.S. Amateur.
tourBios.personal: Favorite athlete is Peyton Manning... If he weren't playing golf, he would be a professional tennis player... Favorite golf course he has played is Royal Melbourne in Australia... Favorite teams growing up were the Dallas Cowboys and the Texas A&M Aggies... Favorite entertainer is George Strait... Would like to trade places with Justin Timberlake for a day… Twitter and Instagram: @jsrussell88
